      "source": [
        "# generate 4 datasets\n",
        "x,y = helper.data_gen(task_num=4,seed=61)\n",
        "\n",
        "x1_data = x[0]\n",

        "y2_data = y[1]\n",

        "y4_data = y[3]"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "sGTsTgtW1HkE"
      },
      "source": [
        "class OnlineEWC:\n",
        "  def __init__(self, model: nn.Module, loss=nn.MSELoss()):\n",
        "    self._model = model\n",
        "    self._params = {}\n",
        "    self._fim = {}\n",
        "    self._loss = loss\n",
        "    self._optim = None\n",
        "    self._lambda = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "  def train(self, inputs, labels, lr, alpha = 0.5, lam=0, epochs=500):\n",
        "    self._optim = torch.optim.Adam(self._model.parameters(), lr=lr)\n",
        "\n",
        "    loss_values_x1 = []\n",
        "    self._lambda = lam\n",
        "\n",
        "    # training\n",
        "    for _ in range(epochs):\n",
        "      f = self._model(inputs.float())\n",
        "      regularizer = 0\n",
        "      if len(self._params) != 0:\n",
        "        loss_ewc = 0\n",
        "        for n, p in self._model.named_parameters():\n",
        "          loss_ewc += torch.matmul(self._fim[n].T, (torch.reshape(p, (-1,1)) - torch.reshape(self._params[n], (-1,1))) ** 2)\n",
        "        regularizer += self._lambda * loss_ewc\n",
        "\n",
        "      loss = self._loss(f, labels.unsqueeze(1).float()) + regularizer\n",
        "      self._optim.zero_grad()\n",
        "      loss.backward()\n",
        "      self._optim.step()\n",
        "\n",
        "      # store loss\n",
        "      loss_values_x1.append(loss.item())\n",
        "\n",
        "    for n, p in deepcopy(self._model).named_parameters():\n",
        "      if p.requires_grad:\n",
        "        self._params[n] = p\n",
        "\n",
        "    # update fisher information matrix\n",
        "    f = self._model(inputs.float())\n",
        "    loss = self._loss(f, labels.unsqueeze(1).float())\n",
        "    self._optim.zero_grad()\n",
        "    loss.backward()\n",
        "\n",
        "    temp_fisher = {}\n",
        "    for n, p in self._model.named_parameters():\n",
        "      temp_fisher[n] = torch.reshape(p.grad.data, (-1,1))\n",
        "\n",
        "    for n, p in temp_fisher.items():\n",
        "      if n in self._fim:\n",
        "        self._fim[n] = self._fim[n]*alpha + p**2 * (1-alpha)\n",
        "      else:\n",
        "        self._fim[n] = p**2\n",
        "    return loss_values_x1"
      ],
      "execution_count": 6,
      "outputs": []
    },

      "source": [
        "# training on the 1st dataset\n",

        "lr = 8e-3\n",
        "model1 = helper.MLP(architecture=[1,100,100,100,100,1])\n",
        "loss_f = nn.MSELoss()\n",
        "\n",
        "ewc = OnlineEWC(model1, loss_f)\n",
        "loss1 = ewc.train(x1_data, y1_data, lr, lam=0, epochs=n_epochs)"
      ],
